
For ping...
	Receive:
		purpose:ping
	Send:
		status:yo

For new connection...
	Receive:
		purpose:vgseer
		locality:<local|remote>
		shell:<bash|zsh>
		pid:<pid>
		vgexpand-opts:<string>
			eg. vgexpand-opts:-d -r -a
	Send:
		do:set-title
	Receive:
		status:title-set
	Send:
		do:continue

Status...
	Receive:
		status:<title-set|executing|prompt|lost>
		pwd:<path>
		cmd:<command line>
		order:<pgup|pgdown|etc.>
	Send:
		key:<key>
		file:<path>

To display when active window changes...
	Send:
		win:<window id>       <-- only sent on a context switch
		cmd:<command line>
		<glob data>

